Instruction for expluatation!

1. Build image

EXAMPLE: docker build . -t imagename:version

2. Mount the folder along the path /opencart/

EXAMPLE: docker run imagename -v ./opencart:/opencart/

3. Set variables or stay with default
variables for set and default values instead VAR: default

EXAMPLE: docker run imagename -e OPENCART_USERNAME=admin

# Admin user
OPENCART_USERNAME: admin

# Admin email
OPENCART_EMAIL: email@example.com

# Admin password
OPENCART_PASSWORD: password

OPENCART_HTTP_SERVER: http://localhost/
OPENCART_HOSTNAME: mysql

# Reqired
OPENCART_DB_USERNAME: root
OPENCART_DB_PASSWORD: pass

OPENCART_DATABASE: opencart
OPENCART_PORT: 3306
OPENCART_PREFIX: oc